title: 1974–75 Essex Senior Football League
text:
The 1974–75 Essex Senior Football League season was the fourth in the history of <a href="Essex%20Senior%20Football%20League">Essex Senior Football League</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in England.
